title: Demand Deposits, Individuals, Corporations, and Others, Weekly Reporting Member Banks for New York, NY
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Four Variables--(1)--Orignal Data, 1919-1934 (2)--Original Data, 1934-1939 (3)--Original Data, 1939-1947 (4)--Original Data, 1946-1949. Data Exclude Demand Deposits Of States And Political Subdivisions. Significant Improvement In Coverage Began In July 1947 (See Frb Bulletin Of June 1947, Pp. 692-693). Source: Federal Reserve Board, Federal Reserve Bulletin, July 1947, Pp. 880-881, And Following Monthly Issues.

This NBER data series m14132d appears on the NBER website in Chapter 14 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter14.html.
